            </h2>
            <p class="text-grey subtitle">
                One Profile. Infinite Possibilities. As you complete a module,
                your entire dashboard updates to accelerate your success.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="rewards-grid">
            <div class="perks-col">
                <h3 class="heading-sm">Synchronized Success</h3>
                <div class="divider"></div>
